               feloniously stealing on the <rs id="t18080914-121-cd702" type="crimeDate">23rd of July</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18080914-121-off701 t18080914-121-cd702"></join>, four pieces of silver, called thirty penny Irish tokens
